creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Stories in Black and White by Various.
Read in English by deongines; Malcolm Fisher; Lynne Thompson; Greg Giordano; ToddHW; Wendy Almeida; Rosslyn Carlyle
This is a collection of short mystery stories, written in very different styles by eight different authors. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
